force ssl content "MAY 2013" WordPress Codex "Function Reference"
=================================================================

NAME
----

force ssl content - Whether to force SSL on content.

SYNOPSIS
--------

Whether to force SSL on content.

USAGE
-----

` <?php force_ssl_content( $force ); ?> `

PARAMETERS
----------

 `$force` 
:   ([*string|bool*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String.7Cbool "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*)
    Default: empty string

RETURN VALUES
-------------

 `` `(bool)`{style="color:gray"} 
:   True if forced, false if not forced.

CHANGE LOG
----------

Since: [2.8.5](/Version_2.8.5 "Version 2.8.5")

SOURCE FILE
-----------

`force_ssl_content()` is located in `wp-includes/ms-functions.php`

